title: Tim Neely's Enthusiast Garage
description:
Tim Neely is a man with a very cool collection of weird, fun cars. He's knowedgable, he's owned good cars, bad cars, and now he talks about them on his YouTube channel, Tim's Enthusiast Garage. Other topics include Safari 911s, what the best S2000 is, engine swaps, what to buy for motorcycle towing, and a ton more. 

 

Watch Tim's Channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCSHC8vHIPzE5EaYjHgx1Tmw

This show is available as a video! https://youtu.be/CSF6zC6Rui4

Follow us!

T: @thesmokingtire @zackklapman @timsenthusiastgarage

IG: @thesmokingtire @fakezackklapman @timsenthusiastgarage

 

Check out our merch!
